query:
UPDATE topicos_reuniao_gestores t
INNER JOIN reunioes_gestores r ON t.reuniaoId = r.id
SET t.estado = 'discutido'
WHERE t.estado = 'analisado' 
AND t.reuniaoId IS NOT NULL 
AND DATE(r.data) < CURDATE();
